{"tid":2157807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google拒港府直接索數據  須循外交提出 當中國申請處理","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:46:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c49092064cf3bb4a168ae5d6eb8f97d04d0e47b3","tid":2157807,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8RqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=77d44827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE%2F&h=36711fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nGoogle拒港府直接索數據 <br />\n須循外交提出 當中國申請處理<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港。。。。。。。。。。。Google昨日則宣佈，正式拒絕直接處理港府索取數據的請求，要求當局循外交途徑向美國政府申請取得這些資料，意味香港獲得的待遇將與中國政府同等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gQ0EHspuJw2m3kMcElMMVg-noro=/2109x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YN3N5JSZGBDWLGBTHTW22SD2QM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgQ0EHspuJw2m3kMcElMMVg-noro%3D%2F2109x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYN3N5JSZGBDWLGBTHTW22SD2QM.jpg&h=e197b899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle行政總裁皮查<br />\n<br />\nGoogle在電郵聲明中宣佈，暫時不再直接處理由香港當局提出的數據要求，表示「按照慣例，美國以外的機構可根據外交程序取得刑事調查所需的數據」，又指Google在港版國安法6月生效後，已沒有產生數據，強調他們一直小心處理任何用戶數據的請求，並拒絕範圍太廣泛的要求，以保障用家私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘停法律互助協定難再索取<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YMhkEWGbHmdIlA4O8cCu1pWkjjM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UVNQVTP4J5CVLEGQHNUDFAID3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYMhkEWGbHmdIlA4O8cCu1pWkjjM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUVNQVTP4J5CVLEGQHNUDFAID3Y.jpg&h=4ec530ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警務處長鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》則報道，Google前日已去信香港警方，要求他們根據香港與美國之間的法律互助協定申請取得其數據。這方法須經過美國司法部繁複的手續，須時數周、甚至數個月，程序與中國提出同類請求時相同。<br />\n<br />\n在法律互助協定下。。。。。。。。。。。。令「五眼聯盟」中只餘下美國與香港的法律互助協定仍然生效。但美國總統特朗普上月透露，華府亦正準備中止與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n科技企業過往會。。。。。。。。。。。。。。戶。Google、facebook、Twitter、微軟和Telegram等網企都在港版國安法通過後，紛紛宣佈暫停處理港府要求分享用戶訊息與數據的請求。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，科技企業都知道它們掌握的用戶數據，在港版國安法下都有可能被中國政府截取，採取不合作態度會與當局發生衝突，令法定代表和僱員因而受到懲罰，加上中美關係近期急轉直下，美國企業有可能成為北京政府的報復對象，因此相信它們對抗只是權宜之計，最終只能選擇離開香港。英國《金融時報》早前亦報道，至少一家西方大型科技公司正考慮所有選項，包括撤離香港。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。因此與中國政府關係相對上較好。美國則有國會議員曾經批評Google對中國的態度太寬鬆，質疑這家科技巨擘其實是與中國政府合作的公司。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》/路透社"},{"pid":"a5aaa44c35e98ed63c5dfb815b43f0e75218d96f","tid":2157807,"uid":110562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"有咩分別 咪又係比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcd55fb597b1479fbfb1478d7fd548f58e94f48","tid":2157807,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a812441c4bcbf80ce0e4e38bc83e08af8cb953a","tid":2157807,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e59adebe1731b5f6f0b58df71057ca78e0603e","tid":2157807,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"邱腐乳出黎未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f59ac9836038a67e1da1ea9d9251a3ae30c8ec","tid":2157807,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"廢撚左個政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}